00:08:53.350 --> 00:08:54.630
that you require,

00:08:54.630 --> 00:08:57.370
to get deep sleep, so it's
got to be of high quality,

00:08:57.370 --> 00:08:59.650
and to time that sleep correctly.

00:08:59.650 --> 00:09:01.320
Meaning you can't sleep
during the day one day,

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:02.270
and at night the next day,

00:09:02.270 --> 00:09:03.930
and expect your system to function well.

00:09:03.930 --> 00:09:05.930
